headline: Ameren : Illinois Promotes Jason Klein to Vice President of Electric Operations
summary: Today, Ameren Illinois announced the promotion of Jason Klein to vice president of Electric Operations and Technical Services, according to Lenny Singh, Chairman and President of Ameren Illinois. ...
